name: Donald Rahman
description: A simple man, very humble, cool and nice. loving, caring with allot of affection. very passionate ,Friendly, sense of humour, business savvy, confident, honest, worldly, intelligent, gentleman. I really enjoy business and discussing it, just about any industry since I find that they are all interrelated and similar infrastructures. I am an entrepreneur. I do innovation, development, design, finance, marketing, accounting, investing, real estate, etc, almost everything needed for small business. Politically, I am republican but believe in many of the liberal views and freedoms. I believe in economic freedom too, almost anything that upholds freedom and smaller government.
